title: Project 1: Expository Visualization
description: This visualization is a histogram with bin specific color encoding. Food items from the major grocers (Whole Foods, Target, and Walmart) are aggregated by the feature ‘price percal’ (price per calorie) to make a histogram. The average of the feature ‘FPro’ (Food Processing Score, 0 (minimally processed) to 1 (highly processed)) of each bin is encoded by color.

title: Project 2: Deceptive Visualization
description: Two visualizations with opposing perceptions. Perception 1: California against abortions in comparison to other states based on change in abortion providers. Perception opp1: california for abortion in comparison to other states based on number of abortion providers.

title: NCAA Softball Big West Conference Simulation
